A whole new trailer for The Lion King live action remake has recently been released by Disney Studios. The new trailer for the Jon Favreau directed remake of the 1994 animated blockbuster gives fans a clearer glimpse into the plot of the movie and also shows some of the major charactrs that previous trailers left out like Simba’s notorious uncle Scar among others. Donald Glover, Beyoncé, Billy Eichner, Alfre Woodard, Chiwetel Ejiofor, and John Oliver are among the cast for the movie. The movie is set to be released on July 19th 2019. Watch “The Lion King” trailer via YouTube below;  